comment: Immersive set with smooth transitions and huge crowd energy.
Loved the vocal effects, could have played longer.
Stage design and vocals were flawless, great pop showcase.
Energetic but a few tracks sounded rushed.
Vocals were powerful and the band was tight.
Atmospheric lighting fit the melancholy vibe perfectly.
Groovy Afrobeat touches had everyone dancing.
Deep house textures felt cinematic and warm.
Smooth flow and catchy hooks, perfect crowd control.
Classic hits with new twists, great closer set.
